---
const base = '/aurora-digital-foundry';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Ecopetrol Aurora</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=Karla:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    :root{--bg:#0b0f1a;--surface:#111827;--border:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);--text:#e2e8f0;--muted:#64748b;--orange:#f77f00;--green:#10b981;--ff:'Karla',sans-serif;--fh:'Syne',sans-serif;}
    body{font-family:var(--ff);background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);line-height:1.65;}
    a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;}
    .container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px;}
    nav{background:rgba(11,15,26,0.95);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;}
    .nav-inner{height:66px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
    .nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-family:var(--fh);font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:800;}
    .nav-mark{background:var(--orange);width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:900;color:#fff;}
    .nav-links{display:flex;gap:24px;list-style:none;}
    .nav-links a{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--muted);transition:color 0.2s;}
    .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text);}
    .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;padding:10px 22px;border-radius:4px;font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;border:none;font-family:var(--ff);transition:all 0.2s;}
    .btn-primary{background:var(--orange);color:#fff;}
    .btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border);}
    .btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--orange);color:var(--orange);}
    section{padding:80px 0;}
    .tag{display:inline-block;font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);border:1px solid rgba(247,127,0,0.3);padding:3px 12px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:16px;}
    h1{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:16px;}
    h2{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:16px;}
    p{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;}
    /* STATS */
    .stat-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:2px;margin:60px 0;}
    .stat{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:32px 24px;text-align:center;}
    .stat-num{font-family:var(--fh);font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--orange);margin-bottom:8px;}
    .stat-label{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--muted);}
    /* COMPLIANCE */
    .compliance-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:40px;}
    .compliance-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:24px;}
    .comp-icon{font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .comp-title{font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--text);}
    .comp-desc{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin:0;}
    .comp-status{display:inline-block;font-size:0.62rem;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:2px;margin-top:10px;background:rgba(16,185,129,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.2);color:var(--green);}
    footer{background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:28px 0;}
    .footer-bar{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted);}
    @media(max-width:900px){.nav-links{display:none;}.stat-grid,.compliance-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}}
    @media(max-width:600px){.stat-grid,.compliance-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<nav><div class="container"><div class="nav-inner">
  <a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/`} class="nav-logo"><div class="nav-mark">EC</div>· ECOPETROL</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/branches`}>Branches</a></li>
    <li><a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/prices`}>Prices</a></li>
    <li><a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/lpg`}>LPG</a></li>
    <li><a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/fleet`}>Fleet</a></li>
    <li><a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/about`} style="color:var(--orange)">About</a></li>
    <li><a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/contact`}>Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/fleet`} class="btn btn-primary">Fleet Accounts</a>
</div></div></nav>

<section style="padding-top:60px">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tag">About</div>
    <h1>Aurora Province's<br/>Fuel Infrastructure.</h1>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:60px;">
      <div>
        <p>Ecopetrol Gasoline Station has been supplying fuel and LPG across Aurora Province for TODO: years. What started as a single branch in Maria Aurora has grown into an 8-branch network spanning the breadth of the province.</p>
        <p>We serve retail motorists, residential LPG customers, fleet operators, government agencies, and commercial businesses — the full spectrum of Aurora's fuel needs under one network.</p>
        <p>As an authorized Solane LPG showroom operator, we extend beyond fuel to provide safe, reliable gas supply to homes, restaurants, resorts, and institutions across our coverage areas.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Our operations are fully compliant with Department of Energy regulations. Each branch maintains current Certificates of Compliance, and our team adheres to established fuel handling, storage, and safety protocols.</p>
        <p>TODO: Additional company history details to be provided by client — founding year, parent entity, ownership, key milestones.</p>
        <a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/contact`} class="btn btn-ghost" style="margin-top:8px;">Contact the Team →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stat-grid">
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">8+</div><div class="stat-label">Branch locations across Aurora</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">TODO</div><div class="stat-label">Years serving Aurora Province</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">4</div><div class="stat-label">Fuel products available</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">5+</div><div class="stat-label">Municipalities covered</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tag">Compliance & Certification</div>
    <h2>Operating to Standard.</h2>
    <p style="max-width:560px;">Every Ecopetrol branch operates under current Department of Energy guidelines. Compliance is not a checkbox — it is how we protect our customers, our communities, and our people.</p>
    <div class="compliance-grid">
      <div class="compliance-card">
        <div class="comp-icon">📋</div>
        <div class="comp-title">DOE Certificate of Compliance</div>
        <p class="comp-desc">All branch locations operate under current DOE Certificates of Compliance as required for retail fuel stations in the Philippines.</p>
        <span class="comp-status">Active — All Branches</span>
      </div>
      <div class="compliance-card">
        <div class="comp-icon">🔥</div>
        <div class="comp-title">Solane Authorized Distributor</div>
        <p class="comp-desc">Official Solane LPG showroom authorization. Our LPG handling staff are trained in DOE-compliant storage, transport, and delivery protocols.</p>
        <span class="comp-status">Authorized</span>
      </div>
      <div class="compliance-card">
        <div class="comp-icon">🛡️</div>
        <div class="comp-title">Safety & Emergency Protocols</div>
        <p class="comp-desc">Branch staff are trained in fire safety, emergency response, and fuel spill containment. Emergency contact numbers are posted at all locations.</p>
        <span class="comp-status">Trained Personnel</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <h2>Ready to work with us?</h2>
    <p style="max-width:440px;margin:0 auto 32px;">Whether you're a daily motorist, a household LPG customer, or a fleet operator — Ecopetrol Aurora is your fuel infrastructure partner in Aurora Province.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/fleet`} class="btn btn-primary">Open Fleet Account →</a>
      <a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/contact`} class="btn btn-ghost">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer><div class="container"><div class="footer-bar">
  <span>© 2026 Ecopetrol Gasoline Station · Aurora Province</span>
  <a href={`${base}/clients/ecopetrol-aurora/`}>← Back to Home</a>
</div></div></footer>
</body>
</html>
